    @Embeddable
@VoDml(id="coords:PolCoordinate",
       role=dataType)
public abstract class PolCoordinate
extends Coordinate
implements org.ivoa.vodml.jpa.JPAManipulations
    Abstract head of the polarization coordinate types. Current use cases only require support for discrete polarization states, however, we include this head class to facilitate extension for other types (eg: polarization fraction and angle). dataType: PolCoordinate
